LOCUS       VSVG_tag                  11 aa            linear   UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  VSVG_tag — 11-aa epitope tag (YTDIEMNRLGK) from the cytoplasmic tail
            of Vesicular stomatitis Indiana virus glycoprotein; detected by the
            P5D4 monoclonal antibody for immunodetection, immunoprecipitation,
            and affinity purification..
